subproject.description:
(1)	Diagnostic of earthquake risk perception and of the relevant socio-economic environment in northern Haiti;
(2)	Building and infrastructure assessment and proposed retrofitting solutions for main building types;
(3)	Earthquake action plan for the 3 main cities of northern Haiti;
(4)	Training of construction professionals (from masons to engineers, both public and private sector);
(5)	Education and outreach to the general public with an emphasis on schools and hospitals.
